  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.8">
<l>māṟi māṟip palapiṟappum piṟantaṭiyai yaṭaintuḷḷan tēṟi</l>
<l>yīṟi liṉpat tiruveḷḷam yāṉmūḻkiṉaṉ</l>
<l>pāṟip pāṟi yacurartam palkuḻāṅka ṇīṟeḻap pāyppaṟavaiyoṉ</l>
<l>ṟēṟi vīṟṟiruntā yuṉṉai yeṉṉu ṇīkkē lentāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After being changed [and] changed, being born in many births I reached servantship, [my] heart believing,</l>
<l>I dived into a great flood of endless pleasure.</l>
<l>O you who sit in distinction, mounted on the bird, pouncing, scattering all about</l>
<l>the many troupes of Asuras, don’t reject my heart, our father.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
